      <title>经济主管表示，欧盟需要自己的财政部来发行欧洲债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/eu-needs-its-own-treasury-to-issue-eurobonds-economy-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟经济负责人表示，欧盟应建立一个中央财政部，通过发行欧元债券为共同物品提供资金，因为欧盟面临着支持其国防部门的大规模支出需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/eu-needs-its-own-treasury-to-issue-eurobonds-economy-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:09:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登与岸田加强防务联盟，着眼于中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/biden-kishida-to-strengthen-defense-alliance-with-eye-on-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级政府官员表示，美国总统乔·拜登和日本首相岸田文雄计划成立一个国防工业委员会，并允许日本造船厂工人对美国海军舰艇进行更多维护工作，以巩固两国的军事联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/biden-kishida-to-strengthen-defense-alliance-with-eye-on-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国派遣五年来最高级别官员访问平壤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/china-sends-highest-ranking-official-to-pyongyang-in-five-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将从周四开始派遣近五年来最高级别的代表团访问朝鲜，平壤与俄罗斯的关系越来越密切。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/china-sends-highest-ranking-official-to-pyongyang-in-five-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:55:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国国防部长呼吁放松债务限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/german-defense-chief-calls-for-loosening-of-debt-restrictions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托利斯大力支持改革限制联邦政府新借款的规则，以帮助为国家武装部队的彻底改革提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/german-defense-chief-calls-for-loosening-of-debt-restrictions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:14:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党誓言打击“逃税者”，为健康承诺提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/labour-vows-tax-dodger-crackdown-to-fill-hole-in-fiscal-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[影子财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯承诺，如果工党赢得即将到来的大选，将加强对非定居居民的打击，并扩大税务合规调查，因为她试图填补英国反对派支出计划中的缺口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/labour-vows-tax-dodger-crackdown-to-fill-hole-in-fiscal-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡梅伦游说特朗普打破美国对乌克兰援助的障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/cameron-lobbies-trump-to-break-us-roadblocks-to-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦飞往佛罗里达州会见唐纳德·特朗普，英国试图让共和党总统候选人在众议院的盟友支持对乌克兰的进一步军事援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/cameron-lobbies-trump-to-break-us-roadblocks-to-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于伊斯兰主义者对加沙的强烈反对，土耳其限制对以色列的出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/turkey-restricts-exports-to-israel-over-gaza-air-drop-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列反对土耳其向加沙地带提供援助以及总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安因维持贸易关系而受到批评后，土耳其宣布限制对以色列的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/turkey-restricts-exports-to-israel-over-gaza-air-drop-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚任命临时内阁为六月快速投票做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/bulgaria-appoints-interim-cabinet-to-prepare-for-june-snap-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚总统鲁门·拉德夫任命了一个临时内阁，为巴尔干国家六月举行的提前选举做好准备，这是三年多来的第六次投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/bulgaria-appoints-interim-cabinet-to-prepare-for-june-snap-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:02:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国批准振兴房地产业的新措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/thailand-approves-new-measures-to-boost-sagging-property-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国政府推出了一系列新措施，包括削减财产登记和转让费用，以重振该国的住宅房地产市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/thailand-approves-new-measures-to-boost-sagging-property-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:25:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰 Naftogaz 在俄罗斯袭击后向天然气交易商示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ukraine-s-naftogaz-courts-gas-traders-after-russian-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管俄罗斯最近对其天然气基础设施发动攻击，乌克兰最大的能源公司仍希望今年与欧洲天然气贸易商达成更多协议，以增加燃料储存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ukraine-s-naftogaz-courts-gas-traders-after-russian-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:52:36 GMT</pubDate>
